text:
[Verse]
The lights up in the sky
Twinkling in the night
Stars are shining bright
Painting dreams in sight

[Verse 2]
The moon it whispers low
Tales of long ago
Waves that ebb and flow
Things we used to know

[Chorus]
Starry night so high
Glowing like a sigh
Catch a shooting light
Wishes come alive

[Verse 3]
In the quiet breeze
Leaves rustle with ease
Moments meant to seize
Sunlight through the trees

[Chorus]
Starry night so high
Glowing like a sigh
Catch a shooting light
Wishes come alive

[Verse 4]
Footsteps in the dark
Hearts begin to spark
Finding where we are
Reaching for a star
title: Starry Night
